data.description: SELLER IS OFFERING $5,000 TOWARDS CLOSING COSTS OR IMPROVEMENTS WITH ACCEPTABLE OFFER ! THEY HAVE EVEN ENHANCED THE PRICE! Welcome to this charming home located in Simpsonville, SC. This beautiful property features fresh paint throughout, giving it a modern and inviting feel. One of the standout features of this home is the absence of an HOA, allowing you the freedom to personalize and enjoy your property without any additional restrictions. Situated on almost half an acre of land, this home offers ample space for outdoor activities and potential expansion. The backyard is fully fenced, providing privacy and security for you, your family, and your pets. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a stunning wood-burning fireplace, perfect for cozy evenings and creating a warm ambiance during the colder months. The fireplace serves as a focal point in the living area, creating a cozy and inviting atmosphere for gatherings and relaxation. The interior of the home is thoughtfully designed, with a layout that maximizes space and functionality. The fresh paint throughout the home adds a touch of elegance and allows for a seamless transition between rooms. Outside you will find a beautiful outbuilding to store your lawn equipment and planters to grow your own veggies! Located in Simpsonville, SC, this home offers the perfect balance of suburban living with easy access to nearby amenities, schools, shopping centers, and parks! Schedule your showing today!
